						<div class="postbody"><div class="quotetitle">pubby wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">You don't need &quot;Overarguments&quot; if you lift &quot;Argumentpush&quot; out of the subroutine and put it somewhere else.</div><br />That could hurt readability though, since the values would be written somewhere else than place where they're used. In ca65 you could solve this by creating a segment for these &quot;trampolines&quot;, and temporarily switch to them just to setup the parameters.</div>

